    "title": "Assignment 1",
    "section": "",
    "text": "In this video, the speakers discuss the relationship between data science and industrial engineering. They explain how data analysis, programming, and statistical thinking are becoming essential skills for industrial engineers.\nThe conversation highlights that modern industrial engineers must be able to work with large datasets, interpret results, and support decision-making using data-driven approaches.",
