  {
    "objectID": "assignments/assignment-1.html#open-ended-question",
    "href": "assignments/assignment-1.html#open-ended-question",
    "title": "Assignment 1",
    "section": "Open-Ended Question",
    "text": "Open-Ended Question\nQuestion:\nWhy is data science becoming increasingly important for industrial engineers?\nAnswer:\nData science is becoming more important for industrial engineers because many industrial problems now require data-driven decision making. Engineers need to analyze data, improve systems, optimize processes, and support better decisions using quantitative evidence.",
