    "section": "Multiple-Choice Question",
    "text": "Multiple-Choice Question\nQuestion:\nWhich of the following is emphasized in the video as an important part of data science?\nA. Only writing code\nB. Statistical thinking and problem solving\nC. Graphic design\nD. Learning foreign languages only\nCorrect Answer:\nB. Statistical thinking and problem solving",
