    "section": "Brief Summary",
    "text": "Brief Summary\nIn this video, the speakers discuss the relationship between data science and industrial engineering. They explain that industrial engineers are increasingly expected to work with data, develop analytical thinking skills, and use programming tools to solve real-world problems.\nThe discussion also emphasizes that data science is not only about coding. It also requires understanding the business problem, interpreting the results correctly, and communicating insights clearly. The video highlights the importance of combining technical knowledge with practical decision-making skills.",
